e scaling with $n$. This\nbehavior is expected to be universal for a wide collection of combinatorial\nproblems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Feb 2007 01:47:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Nov 2008 07:01:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-18"}
